{"tid":1439772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺最近TVB已經冇乜再提跨平台總收視？","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:26:24.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d08d479412ff75dacfb5121f4139ee12e7ae12a","tid":1439772,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"平時會拎跨平台總收視嚟打飛機，最近真係唔見佢拎出嚟講，係咪因為收視跌到仆直所以低到拎唔到出嚟打飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫的收視持續下跌，昨日無綫公佈7月22日至28日的收視成績，可謂慘不忍睹，一向深得觀眾支持的《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》，竟然跌破25點，跨平台總收視只有<span style=\"color: red;\">24.4點</span>（約157萬觀眾收看），相信是近半年來的新低點。譚俊彥和張振朗的新劇《包青天再起風雲》首周播出，不過跨平台總收視只有<span style=\"color: red;\">21.9點</span>（約144萬觀眾收看），暫時成為19年無綫黃金檔三線劇首周最低收視的劇集。"},{"pid":"69ae10827085c6611de336a4ff1899efc7e64380","tid":1439772,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"收視已經唔係重要，近排師奶都無心情睇電視啦<br />\n一定要罷買佢81台同新聞台所有廣告"},{"pid":"064431797d3df12a2009ac0983424abea5984460","tid":1439772,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0486cde062200064ab666a419d5316322c8c35","tid":1439772,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"064431797d3df12a2009ac0983424abea5984460","tid":1439772,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"viu會"}]}